Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.77,0:00:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.06,0:00:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.36,0:00:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. It's a warship.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.78,0:00:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell Gorm. Hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.74,0:00:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. Look closely.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.79,0:00:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,They're Askeladd's ships.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.50,0:00:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We finally made it back to the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.01,0:00:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we survived another year.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.80,0:00:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And you still haven't died, Bjorn.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.55,0:01:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We went pretty far.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.43,0:01:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.18,0:01:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. It's the sheep. They're still grazing them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.44,0:01:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,They're trying to fatten them up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.19,0:01:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like Gorm's still stingy as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.33,0:01:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Men.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.66,0:01:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for your hard work this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.71,0:01:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Enjoy the winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.06,0:03:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.23,0:03:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,NOVEMBER 1012 AD
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.27,0:03:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,FEUDAL LORD GORM'S VILLAGE \NJUTLAND PENINSULA
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.86,0:03:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,There's so much treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.65,0:03:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,They had a huge victory \Nin the land of the Franks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.82,0:03:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,BEYOND THE EDGE OF THE SEA
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.20,0:03:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm impressed, Askeladd.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.74,0:03:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,-I heard some men died this year. \N-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.74,0:03:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if they're going to look for new sailors again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.20,0:03:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn. I can't wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.08,0:03:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm going to sail, I want to sail with Askeladd.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.79,0:03:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot. You'd die within three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.18,0:03:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. Say you're sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.27,0:03:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with that kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.03,0:04:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready? One, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.12,0:04:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Askeladd.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.29,0:04:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.87,0:04:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.29,0:04:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.54,0:04:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. I brought you some necklaces.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.63,0:04:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,-I'll take it. \N-I want a ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.01,0:04:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Uncle Gorm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.59,0:04:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The girls here aren't modest at all. It's wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.06,0:04:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here to talk about a serious matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.52,0:04:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you ready to listen?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.27,0:04:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.19,0:04:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The cost to feed one of your men
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.90,0:04:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,is one and one-fourth silver coins per day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.19,0:04:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You have 97 men,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.57,0:04:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,so that's 121 coins in total--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.82,0:04:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to talk about money again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.20,0:04:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The price of pork increased this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.74,0:04:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to eat pork every day, \Nthen you would need...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.08,0:04:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Beer is charged separately.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.83,0:04:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you add in the cost of lodging and firewood...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.29,0:05:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Uncle, stop worrying.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.92,0:05:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We earned a lot this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.01,0:05:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Give my men plenty of booze and food.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.51,0:05:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.30,0:05:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I was waiting to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.06,0:05:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll buy you a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.60,0:05:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring the celebratory drinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.14,0:05:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We have some good wine, right? Bring it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.23,0:05:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two, three...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.48,0:05:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Uncle. Do you really love money so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.03,0:05:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there anyone who doesn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.49,0:05:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Money is great. Just looking at it makes me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.33,0:05:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hordaland. What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.33,0:05:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up, and bring the wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.55,0:05:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.88,0:05:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, dear. What a troublesome woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.64,0:05:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What a weird name.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.35,0:05:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That slave girl. Hordaland?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.89,0:05:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,-It's the name of a region in Norway. \N-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.52,0:05:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I bought her recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.56,0:06:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,She's the daughter of a feudal lord, \Nbut her family lost a battle, and fell to ruin.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.40,0:06:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a beautiful girl, and she was expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.20,0:06:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But she's slow at work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.07,0:06:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Rich girls are useless. \NThey just have a lot of pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.54,0:06:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,-By the way, Uncle... \N-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.67,0:06:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I ask you to be my witness?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.38,0:06:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scheduled for a duel before dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.55,0:06:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,A duel?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.79,0:06:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.47,0:06:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not the slave's fault that she's useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.55,0:06:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just bad at using her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.81,0:06:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.14,0:06:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You can make use of anyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.52,0:06:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,with the right approach.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.03,0:06:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.98,0:06:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.03,0:06:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.61,0:06:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do it, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.36,0:06:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it. Don't lose to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.54,0:07:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,In the name of Odin,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.67,0:07:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the duel between Thorfinn \Nand Askeladd is about to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.67,0:07:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Each man may choose their own weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.46,0:07:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If you fight with honor,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.34,0:07:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,your soul shall pass through the gates of Valhalla, \Neven if you shall die.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.01,0:07:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.47,0:07:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He's one of Askeladd's men?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.48,0:07:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe he'd let even someone \Nlike me sail with him too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.98,0:07:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,-He's kind of cute, right? \N-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.11,0:07:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Askeladd has more money. And he's strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.53,0:07:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason for this duel is for Thorfinn \Nto avenge his father's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.95,0:07:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,-Are there any objections? \N-No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.29,0:07:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.42,0:07:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Then begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.71,0:07:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Unbelievable. Thorfinn's so stubborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.97,0:07:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.89,0:07:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.14,0:07:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.68,0:07:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.81,0:08:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,got taller.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.90,0:08:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,How old are you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.07,0:08:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You were still only this tall back then--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.11,0:08:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Thorfinn attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.99,0:08:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,He got up close.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.79,0:08:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You should go along with making small-talk...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.96,0:08:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,with old men.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.01,0:08:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,-He got up. \N-He's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.09,0:08:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He sent him flying with a single hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.39,0:08:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot. Thorfinn jumped.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.68,0:08:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,He knows that the one with the dagger has the advantage \Nat close range.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.06,0:08:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He's stronger now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.56,0:08:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,-Nice, kid. \N-Askeladd.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.11,0:08:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.50,0:09:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,He's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.76,0:09:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.18,0:09:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.60,0:09:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Get him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.77,0:09:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.65,0:09:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Thorfinn.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.44,0:09:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Your father... What was his name?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.74,0:09:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Tho... Tho... Tho...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.70,0:09:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Thors.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.41,0:09:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Thors. That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.42,0:09:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Getting old is making me forgetful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.51,0:09:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.47,0:10:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you're in the middle of getting revenge, \Nso I feel bad saying this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.10,0:10:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I've killed a lot of people, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.73,0:10:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't quite remember your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.65,0:10:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I really kill him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.32,0:10:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I kill Thoril?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.32,0:10:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. Do you remember how I killed him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.12,0:10:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What if...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.37,0:10:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, maybe you're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.41,0:10:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.91,0:10:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If you had fought him with honor,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.21,0:10:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,my father would never have lost to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.01,0:10:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,During that fight,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.26,0:10:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.43,0:10:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You took me hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.56,0:10:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right. I remember now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.40,0:10:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,He's that idiot who put down his sword \Nto save a kid's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.09,0:11:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What did he do just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.39,0:11:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get so worked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.55,0:11:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't trained enough, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.93,0:11:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.37,0:11:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Bjorn. Pick him up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.62,0:11:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.00,0:11:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.83,0:11:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.13,0:11:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.88,0:12:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to eat some lamb breast.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.17,0:12:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Roasted with herbs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.24,0:12:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been waiting for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.16,0:12:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.04,0:12:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. Aren't you supposed to guard the ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.67,0:12:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I got out of it. Thorfinn said he doesn't want to switch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.13,0:12:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean he's in a bad mood because he lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.59,0:12:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,He's always been like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.10,0:12:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,He feels comfortable there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.97,0:12:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It used to be his father's ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.44,0:12:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Just leave him alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.44,0:13:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.40,0:13:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Askeladd.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.57,0:13:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's duel was amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.16,0:13:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.21,0:13:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You threw him at the end, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.87,0:13:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you do that? That was so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.92,0:13:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know, captain...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.59,0:13:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure about taking a kid \Nlike him sailing with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.38,0:13:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What if he attacks you while you sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.97,0:13:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.18,0:13:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,He could never do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.98,0:13:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.65,0:13:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a warrior, too, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.69,0:13:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He'd only accept victory with honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.11,0:13:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He's held back by his past, and his pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.67,0:13:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's you again, Horda.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.46,0:14:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in the way. Clean it up. Hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.80,0:14:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not a noblewoman anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.55,0:14:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand up, you clumsy girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.97,0:14:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.60,0:14:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If I had to live without pride,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.81,0:14:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd rather kill myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.73,0:14:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Did I say something funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.19,0:14:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,No. It's not you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.99,0:14:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.78,0:14:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.08,0:14:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget, you're just a slave.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.16,0:14:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The guy who's a slave to money holds a whip,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.33,0:14:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and pretends to be the master \Nof the slave he bought with his money.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.88,0:14:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He just doesn't realize it himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.01,0:14:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone is a slave to something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.24,0:15:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You upset?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.54,0:15:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.43,0:15:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. Crybaby.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.03,0:15:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it hurt, kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.99,0:15:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to get revenge?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.58,0:15:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you're my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.74,0:16:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If I told you not to seek revenge, you wouldn't listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.92,0:16:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.75,0:16:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.05,0:16:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you'll just have to realize it on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.76,0:16:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.76,0:16:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have any enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.81,0:16:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No one has any enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.48,0:16:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,A true warrior doesn't need a sword...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.13,0:16:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Gorm told me
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.18,0:16:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,to bring you some food.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.28,0:17:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. Are you a slave too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.66,0:17:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.96,0:17:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you're eating out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.33,0:17:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a warrior.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.17,0:17:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Unlike you,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.76,0:17:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I can eat wherever I like.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.05,0:17:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.55,0:17:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But I feel like you're the same as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.56,0:17:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no idea how a slave feels.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.10,0:17:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,If I were you, I'd kill Gorm and run away. \NI'd kill everyone who came after me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.73,0:17:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill him? I could never kill someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.45,0:17:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you'll be a slave for the rest of your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.91,0:18:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.87,0:18:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If I run away...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.75,0:18:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Run away as far as I can...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.84,0:18:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If I run away to the other side of the ocean,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.80,0:18:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,then what's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.89,0:18:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,There's probably nothing there, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.43,0:18:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how far I go, it'd be the same as here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.85,0:18:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Just filled with wars, and slave traders.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.16,0:18:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Far west,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.25,0:18:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,across the sea,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.88,0:18:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,there is a land called
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.25,0:18:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Vinland.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.30,0:18:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.26,0:18:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And fertile.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.80,0:19:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,A faraway land,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.55,0:19:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,where neither slave traders \Nnor the flames of war reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.81,0:19:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,No one would be able
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.18,0:19:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,to find you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.48,0:19:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Does such a place truly exist?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.10,0:19:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,AUGUST 1013 AD \NVICINITY OF JELLING, DENMARK
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.99,0:20:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The finest warriors \Nfrom clans all over Denmark are gathering.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.45,0:20:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,In addition,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.53,0:20:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,four of our Jomsvikings brigades are hastening \Nto join them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.71,0:20:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is proceeding as planned
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.21,0:20:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,for the upcoming campaign.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.68,0:20:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The time has finally come.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.64,0:20:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We must show those insolent English scoundrels
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.93,0:20:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,the power of the king.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.39,0:20:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.31,0:20:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.73,0:20:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We will fight without yield \Nto achieve Your Highness's goal of capturing England.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.19,0:20:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Canute?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.11,0:20:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He's here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.20,0:20:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.24,0:20:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,His Highness has already arrived in Jelling.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.95,0:20:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,He's resting to prepare to march.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.37,0:20:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Highness. Are you sure, \Nyou don't want to change your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.25,0:20:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Ragnar.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.92,0:21:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need for His Highness Canute \Nto come along.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.13,0:21:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a candidate to succeed the throne.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.93,0:21:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I must give him a chance \Nto display valor on the battlefield,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.55,0:21:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,so that he doesn't lose to his brother Harald.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.68,0:21:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But His Highness doesn't \Nhave much experience on the battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.73,0:21:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ragnar.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.65,0:21:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm worried for Canute's safety as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.11,0:21:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,However, we're the leaders of the Vikings.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.65,0:21:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,If we don't demonstrate valor, \Nthe people will not follow us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.99,0:21:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We shall sail tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.60,0:21:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,In August of 1013 AD,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.94,0:22:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,a Danish and Viking fleet, led by King Sweyn,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.61,0:22:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,invaded the northern part of England, \Nstarting from the Humber River.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.57,0:22:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,In the region of Gainsborough,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.45,0:22:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,five major cities were taken,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.41,0:22:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and the main army continued \Ntheir advance south over land with great speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.96,0:22:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,They overran the region, \Nas they continued their advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.92,0:22:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,However, their steady advance came \Nto a temporary halt...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.97,0:22:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,LONDON
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.68,0:22:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,at the merchant town of London.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.14,0:22:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,OCTOBER 1013 AD \NLONDON, ENGLAND
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.96,0:23:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Bring it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.01,0:23:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a fun war.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.77,0:00:26.02,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,とーとーとー。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.06,0:00:29.61,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,とーとーとー\Nあ？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.36,0:00:34.11,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おい！軍船が来た！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.78,0:00:36.07,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ゴルム様に早く…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.74,0:00:38.74,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,待てよ。よく見ろ。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.79,0:00:41.50,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,アシェラッドさんの船だ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.50,0:00:51.51,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ふぇー。やっと村か
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.01,0:00:54.72,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,やれやれ。今年も生き延びたぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.80,0:00:57.47,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,また死に損なったなビョルン
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.55,0:01:00.35,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,随分遠出しちまったからなぁ…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.43,0:01:01.27,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あん？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.18,0:01:05.35,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おい羊だ。まだ草を食わせてやがる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.44,0:01:09.11,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,少しでも太らせようとしてんだろ。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.19,0:01:12.82,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ゴルム叔父のドケチ根性は相変わらずのようだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.33,0:01:22.58,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,野郎ども！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.66,0:01:24.62,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,今年もご苦労だった！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.71,0:01:27.17,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,大いに冬を楽しんでくれたまえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.06,0:03:08.02,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あっちだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.86,0:03:15.98,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,すげぇお宝だなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.65,0:03:19.74,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,フランクの地で大勝利だったとさ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.80,0:03:21.24,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,さすがアシェラッドさんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.74,0:03:24.66,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,今年も何人か死んだってよ\Nマジか！？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.74,0:03:27.37,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,また新しい乗組員募集するかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.20,0:03:30.00,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ちくしょオ血が騒ぐ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.08,0:03:32.71,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,乗るならやっぱアシェラッドさんの船だぜ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.79,0:03:35.96,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,バーカ。お前じゃ3日であの世行きだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.18,0:03:43.30,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おい待てよ！謝れよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.27,0:03:57.90,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,な…なんだよあのガキ…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.03,0:04:06.58,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いくよ！うん！せーの！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.12,0:04:09.20,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,アシェラッドさまーっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.29,0:04:11.33,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おかえりなさーい！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.87,0:04:14.21,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いよぉ！お嬢さん方。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.29,0:04:15.88,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,カワイイねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.54,0:04:19.63,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ほ～ら！おみやげの首飾りだよォ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.63,0:04:23.13,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,キャーッ！\Nあたし指輪がいい！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.01,0:04:25.51,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ゴルムの叔父貴よ。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.59,0:04:29.52,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ここの女たちは慎みってもんがなくて実にいいな！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.06,0:04:32.43,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,女よりマジメな話じゃ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.52,0:04:33.64,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ちゃんと聞かんか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.27,0:04:35.10,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,よいか？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.19,0:04:37.82,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前の手下の1日の食い物代が
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.90,0:04:40.53,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,銀貨1枚と1/4だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.19,0:04:43.49,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,手下は97人だから
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.57,0:04:45.74,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,全部で121枚と…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.82,0:04:48.12,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,まーた金勘定かよ…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.20,0:04:50.66,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,今年は豚が値上がりした。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.74,0:04:53.41,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,毎日豚を食うのならさらに～…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.08,0:04:55.75,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ビールは別料金で
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.83,0:04:58.21,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,これに宿代と薪代を加えて…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.29,0:05:00.84,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,叔父貴。心配するな。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.92,0:05:02.55,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,今年の稼ぎも上々だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.01,0:05:06.43,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,手下どもには酒もエサも十分にやってくれ。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.51,0:05:08.22,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,金は払うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.30,0:05:10.97,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,それが聞きたかったんじゃよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.06,0:05:12.06,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,一杯おごろう
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.60,0:05:14.06,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おい祝い酒だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.14,0:05:16.81,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いいワインがあったじゃろ。これへもて
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.23,0:05:20.40,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ひー…ふー…みー…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.48,0:05:22.99,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,叔父貴…そんなに金が好きか？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.03,0:05:25.90,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,嫌いな奴がおるか？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.49,0:05:30.58,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,金はいい…見てるだけで気持ちが明るうなる
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.33,0:05:36.67,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,これホルザランド何しとる。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.33,0:05:39.21,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,はようワインを持ってこんか！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.55,0:05:42.38,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,はい…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.88,0:05:46.05,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,やれやれ…困った女だ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.64,0:05:50.26,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,変な名だな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.35,0:05:53.81,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あの奴隷女。ホルザランド
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.89,0:05:56.44,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ノルウェーの土地の名だ\Nああ。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.52,0:05:58.06,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,最近買ったんじゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.56,0:06:03.48,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,領主の血筋らしいが戦に\N負けてお家が滅んだとか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.40,0:06:08.11,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,べっぴんだし高かったんじゃがなぁ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.20,0:06:09.99,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,仕事の覚えは悪いし。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.07,0:06:15.50,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,まったく…\Nお嬢様育ちは気位ばかり高くて役に立たん
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.54,0:06:18.58,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ところで叔父貴\Nむ？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.67,0:06:20.63,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,立会人頼んでもいいかな。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.38,0:06:24.46,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,晩飯前に決闘の予約が入っててさ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.55,0:06:25.51,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,決闘？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.79,0:06:28.04,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,それとな。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.47,0:06:31.47,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,役に立たないのは奴隷のせいじゃないぜ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.55,0:06:33.72,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あんたの使い方がヘタなんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.81,0:06:34.89,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんじゃと？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.14,0:06:38.52,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どんな奴にでも
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.52,0:06:42.36,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,上手に使うコツってのがあるもんさ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.03,0:06:45.90,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,急げ急げ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.98,0:06:46.94,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,何だ何だ？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.03,0:06:48.53,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,決闘だってよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.61,0:06:50.28,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,がんばれ小僧ー！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.36,0:06:52.66,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,やったれー！負けんなよー！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.54,0:07:00.58,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あーこれよりーオーディンの名においてー
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.67,0:07:04.00,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,トルフィン対アシェラッドの決闘を執り行うー
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.67,0:07:07.38,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,武器はおのおの好きに選んでよい。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.46,0:07:09.26,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,互いに誇りを持って戦えば
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.34,0:07:14.51,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,死してなおその魂はヴァルハラの扉を開くであろう
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.01,0:07:16.39,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,マジかよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.47,0:07:18.73,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あいつがアシェラッド兵団の一員だって！？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.48,0:07:22.35,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,やっぱオレでも船に乗せてもらえるんじゃねーの？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.98,0:07:26.02,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ちょっとカワイくない？あの子\Nえー。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.11,0:07:28.99,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,アシェラッドさんの方がお金あるし強いよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.53,0:07:34.87,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なお決闘の理由はトルフィンによる彼の父親の仇討ちである。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.95,0:07:38.62,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,両者異議はないか？\Nない
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.29,0:07:40.25,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.42,0:07:43.08,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,では始め！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.71,0:07:49.63,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ったくトルフィンも懲りねえな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.68,0:07:59.77,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.81,0:08:02.81,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,背ェ伸びたなァ。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.90,0:08:04.31,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,トシなんぼになった？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.07,0:08:09.82,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あん時はまだお前こんくらいの…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.11,0:08:14.99,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,トルフィンが仕掛けた！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.99,0:08:17.24,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,フトコロに入ったぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.79,0:08:22.71,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,年寄りのっ世間バナシぐらいっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.96,0:08:25.58,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,つきあえよっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.01,0:08:33.01,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,立った！\N何ともねえぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.09,0:08:36.30,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ひとなぎであんなに吹っ飛ばした…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.39,0:08:39.01,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,バカ言え。トルフィンが跳んだんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.68,0:08:42.89,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,くっつけば短剣の方が有利なのを分かってる
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.06,0:08:45.48,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,強くなったなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.56,0:08:48.15,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いいぞコゾーッ！\Nアシェラッドさまー！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.11,0:08:51.49,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,やれやれーっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.50,0:09:04.41,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,うめェ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.76,0:09:13.59,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,くそっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.18,0:09:21.52,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いいぞー！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.60,0:09:23.60,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,やれやれー！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.77,0:09:26.85,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,もうちょっとだ小僧！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.65,0:09:31.86,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なぁトルフィン。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.44,0:09:37.57,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前の親父…あれ？なんつったかな…？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.74,0:09:42.62,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,えっと…トートー…トーケ…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.70,0:09:43.83,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,トールズだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.41,0:09:48.33,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,トールズ！そうそう！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.42,0:09:51.21,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いかんなァ。年とると物忘れがなァ。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.51,0:09:57.38,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いやでもさァ、
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.47,0:10:03.02,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,実際こうやって仇討ち～\Nなんてやってる最中に申し訳ないけどほら。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.10,0:10:05.64,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,オレいっぱい殺してるからさ。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.73,0:10:09.52,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,思い出せないんだよ。君の父上のこと
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.65,0:10:13.23,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,オレ本当に殺したかなァ？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.32,0:10:15.28,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,トーリルさんを。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.32,0:10:20.03,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なあ。オレどーやって殺したっけ？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.12,0:10:21.28,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ひょっとして
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.37,0:10:23.83,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前の勘違いってことはないかねぇ？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.41,0:10:26.71,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,貴様…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.91,0:10:30.17,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,正々堂々戦えば…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.21,0:10:33.92,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,父上は貴様なんかに負けなかった…！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.01,0:10:38.18,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,貴様はあの時…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.26,0:10:39.30,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,オレを…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.43,0:10:48.48,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,オレを人質に…！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.56,0:10:51.31,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あー！はいはい思い出したァ。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.40,0:10:55.19,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ガキの命と引き換えに剣を捨てたあのバカだァ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.09,0:11:15.75,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,今何した？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.39,0:11:23.47,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,アツくなっちゃダメェ～。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.55,0:11:25.76,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,修行が足りないぜボウヤ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.93,0:11:29.23,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,くっ…くそが…！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.37,0:11:46.54,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ビョルン。肩入れといて
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.62,0:11:47.66,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.00,0:11:51.16,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あ～あ腹減った。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.83,0:11:53.08,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ああそーだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.13,0:11:55.00,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,叔父貴！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.88,0:12:00.09,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,羊の胸肉食いてぇなー。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.17,0:12:01.93,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,香草焼きで
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.24,0:12:26.74,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,待ってました！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.16,0:12:32.96,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,うーさみさみ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.04,0:12:35.58,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あれ？船の見張りは？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.67,0:12:38.63,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,もうけたぜぇ。トルフィンが代わりたくねぇとさ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.13,0:12:42.51,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あ～。負けるとイジける例のヤツか
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.59,0:12:45.76,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ああいうところは昔っから変わらねぇな
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.10,0:12:49.01,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あそこが落ち着くんだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.97,0:12:52.39,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,もともとはアイツの親父の船だからな。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.44,0:12:54.94,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ほっときゃいいさ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.44,0:13:04.32,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,まあまあイケる
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.40,0:13:05.53,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,アシェラッドさん！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.57,0:13:10.08,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,今日の決闘、感動したっス！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.16,0:13:11.58,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あ？そう？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.21,0:13:15.79,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,最後のって投げですよね？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.87,0:13:19.25,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どーやるんすかアレ？カッコよかったなー！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.92,0:13:21.51,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,だけど大将。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.59,0:13:24.30,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あんなガキ船に乗せてヤバくないスか？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.38,0:13:26.89,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,寝込みを襲われでもしたら…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.97,0:13:29.10,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,平気平気。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.18,0:13:31.47,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,アレにはンなことできねぇよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.98,0:13:36.56,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どういうことです？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.65,0:13:39.61,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,奴も一応戦士だからね。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.69,0:13:43.36,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,正々堂々一騎打ちで勝たないとイヤなのさ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.11,0:13:52.20,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,過去とプライドが奴を縛ってるわけだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.67,0:13:59.96,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,またお前かホルザ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.46,0:14:03.21,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,みんなの邪魔だ！さっさと片づけろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.80,0:14:06.47,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いつまで貴族のつもりでおるんじゃお前は！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.55,0:14:09.89,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,立て！立たんか！このノロマめ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.97,0:14:11.97,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,よくわかりませんけど…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.60,0:14:14.72,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,プライドもなく生きるくらいなら
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.81,0:14:17.14,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,自殺しますけどね。オレは
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.73,0:14:22.11,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんです？おかしいですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.19,0:14:23.98,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いやお前じゃねえよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.99,0:14:29.70,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,見てみろ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.78,0:14:31.99,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ひっでぇザマだぜありゃあ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.08,0:14:35.08,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いいかげん奴隷の自覚を持たんか！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.16,0:14:37.25,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,カネの奴隷がムチ持って、
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.33,0:14:41.29,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,カネで買った奴隷に主人ヅラしてやがんの
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.88,0:14:45.96,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,自覚がないだけなのさ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.01,0:14:50.26,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,人間はみんな何かの奴隷だ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.24,0:15:08.57,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いじけてるな
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.54,0:15:17.70,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,父上…！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.43,0:15:37.18,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,や～い。なーきむーしけーむしー
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.03,0:15:48.86,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,くやしいかチビスケ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.99,0:15:51.61,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,仕返ししたいか？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.58,0:15:57.66,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,オレの子だからなぁ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.74,0:16:01.08,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,仕返しすんなって言っても無駄だろうし…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.92,0:16:03.50,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,困ったな…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.75,0:16:06.34,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どう言えばいいのか…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.05,0:16:10.97,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,自分の力で気づくしかないのかもな…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.76,0:16:15.68,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,言っただろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.76,0:16:18.72,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前には敵などいない。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.81,0:16:21.14,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,誰にも敵などいないんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.48,0:16:32.61,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,本当の戦士には剣など…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.13,0:16:54.09,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あの…ゴルム様があなたに…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.18,0:16:56.18,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,食事を持ってけって…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.28,0:17:22.58,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ねぇ…キミも奴隷なの？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.66,0:17:23.87,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あァ？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.96,0:17:26.58,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,だってそんなトコで食べてるし…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.33,0:17:30.09,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,オレは戦士だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.17,0:17:31.67,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あんたと違って
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.76,0:17:33.97,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,メシを食う場所を自由に選べる
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.05,0:17:36.47,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そうなの？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.55,0:17:41.10,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,でもなんだかキミ…私と同じって感じがするから…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.56,0:17:44.35,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,奴隷の気持ちなんざ知るか！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.10,0:17:50.06,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,オレがあんただったらゴルムを殺して逃げる！\N追っ手も全員殺す！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.73,0:17:54.32,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そんな…殺すなんて…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.45,0:17:58.82,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なら一生奴隷でいればいい。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.91,0:18:00.12,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あんたの勝手だ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.87,0:18:08.25,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,逃げて…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.75,0:18:10.75,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どこまでも逃げて
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.84,0:18:13.71,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,海の彼方まで逃げ切ったら…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.80,0:18:16.26,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そこには何があるのかしら…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.89,0:18:22.39,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,きっと何もないわね…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.43,0:18:25.77,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どこまで行ってもここと同じ…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.85,0:18:28.65,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,戦と奴隷商人がいるだけ…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.16,0:18:47.21,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,はるか西…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.25,0:18:49.58,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,海の向こうに…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.88,0:18:52.21,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,“ヴィンランド”という名の…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.25,0:18:54.21,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,土地がある
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.30,0:18:57.17,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そこは暖かく、
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.26,0:18:58.72,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,豊かで、
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.80,0:19:00.47,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,奴隷商人も
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.55,0:19:03.89,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,戦の炎も届かない、遠い地…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.81,0:19:08.10,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そこなら誰も…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.18,0:19:09.56,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,追ってはこれない…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.48,0:19:16.48,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そんなところが…本当に…？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.99,0:20:04.91,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,デンマーク各地より各部族の精鋭たち集結しつつあります
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.45,0:20:06.45,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,加えて我ら
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.53,0:20:10.66,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ヨーム戦士団4個大隊、馳せ参じております
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.71,0:20:14.13,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,この度の大攻勢にあたり、
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.21,0:20:16.13,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,万事滞りなく
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.68,0:20:24.55,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ようやくだ…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.64,0:20:27.39,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,イングランドの不遜な輩どもに
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.93,0:20:30.35,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,王の力を示さねばならぬ…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.39,0:20:32.23,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,はっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.31,0:20:33.65,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,戦士団一同、
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.73,0:20:38.27,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,陛下のイングランド掌握のため尽力する次第であります
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.19,0:20:43.03,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,してクヌートは？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.11,0:20:44.78,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あやつは来ておるな？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.20,0:20:46.16,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,はっ。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.24,0:20:48.87,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,殿下もすでにイェリングに入られ、
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.95,0:20:52.29,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ご出陣に向け英気を養われているとのこと
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.37,0:20:56.17,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,陛下！やはりお考えは変わらぬのでしょうか
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.25,0:20:57.84,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ラグナル殿…！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.92,0:21:01.05,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なにもクヌート殿下がご同行されずとも…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.13,0:21:04.84,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あやつも世継ぎ候補だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.93,0:21:07.47,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,兄のハラルドに劣らぬ武勲の
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.55,0:21:09.60,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,機会を与えねばな
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.68,0:21:14.31,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,しかし恐れながら殿下はまだ戦場でのご経験も浅く…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.73,0:21:16.56,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ラグナルよ…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.65,0:21:19.07,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,余とてクヌートの身は案じておる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.11,0:21:23.57,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,だが我らはヴァイキングの長。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.65,0:21:26.57,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,武勇を示さねば民は従わぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.99,0:21:30.16,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,明朝、出航する
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.60,0:21:56.85,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,西暦1013年8月。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.94,0:22:01.52,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,スヴェン大王率いるデンマーク・ヴァイキング主力艦隊は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.61,0:22:05.36,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,イングランド北部のハンバー川より侵攻を開始
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.57,0:22:08.36,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ゲインズバラにて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.45,0:22:11.33,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,周辺の5大都市を降伏させると
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.41,0:22:16.91,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,その勢いはとどまることなく主力軍はそのまま陸路を南下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.96,0:22:21.79,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,各地を蹂躙しつつ進軍を続けた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.92,0:22:30.89,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,だが…このまま続くと思われた快進撃も、\Nここにきて一時停滞することとなる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.68,0:22:35.56,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,商業都市ロンドンにて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.96,0:23:06.92,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どうしたぁ！もっと攻めてこいよぉ！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.01,0:23:10.13,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,楽しい戦じゃねぇか！
